Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.88,0:00:04.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Will you become my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:06.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:09.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:11.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:13.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:35.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:35.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:39.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was very enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:43.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:43.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.93,0:00:48.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And don't get too involved. Also, don't let others get too involved either. {in chihiro}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:54.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Himura-san, is it wrong for me to tell another person about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:58.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I won't object if it's something that Chihiro has decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:02.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In my personal opinion however,  I do not support it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:05.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:11.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If I do something wrong, I can't even regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:03.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Now then. Onii-chan, it's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:07.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be late if you don't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.78,0:02:21.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, since I already did this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:25.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,whatever happens now is Onii-chan's responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to wake up! {sneak attack dmg boost! critical hit!}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:34.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:37.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your method of waking up a person getting worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:40.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's because your habit of oversleeping is getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:43.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to sleep on the desk because it isn't good for your body, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.94,0:02:47.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice. The deadline is close so it's an emergency. {was "the due date is close so it's emergent." - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:49.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You say that every month.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:53.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Work is good, but Onii-chan's primary job is a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:55.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Being a manga artist is a primary job too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:59.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Put away the excuse and quickly wash your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Or else everyone will find out about your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:20.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, if you don't go to school your attendance record will be in trouble.{to school} {you're to your. - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:21.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're not smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Your grades are bad as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:25.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You have no tenacity{perseverance}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you also lack attendance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:31.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,then it would be the same as saying, "Let me retake my second year."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:34.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then I might be in the same class as Kei next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:38.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you to go to school properly so that won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:41.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you to stop your publications.{series/}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:47.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:48.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:53.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you reading my manga these days?{Do you read my manga these days?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:56.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:59.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't give your thoughts on it anymore.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:03.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But it's embarrassing to tell something like my thoughts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:07.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And also, you get letters from readers even if I don't say anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Shindou Nagi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me by that name outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:12.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can't call me "Onii-chan" either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:19.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fall asleep.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to what the teacher says properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:24.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And listen{loud and properly} attentively when you're called on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, my guardian?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:28.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Hirono-sempai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you unusually early, Hirono...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:35.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:37.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And also coming to school along with your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,As a man did you grow a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my girlfriend, and it is none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:49.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Hirono. Even if a girl isn't your type, it's important to become friendly with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:52.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a girl's friend that is your type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:55.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Also, around the girl's friend might be someone that is more appealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:05:00.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is your reason for meeting girls without discretion because of that strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:02.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just have a broader range.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:05.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Would there be any reliability in the words spoken by such a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you going to classes today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm here, I might as well get an attendance stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:05.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}always...{preferrably have the "I have..." and "Always." show as spoken.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:09.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}had the feeling of emptiness as if I'm lacking something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:15.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get the feeling that there's a color missing from the world that I look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:19.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't know what color is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So even if I want to find the answer, I can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:25.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The hastening heart just eats itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're being very diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm an idiot, I can only look forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:43.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think that there is a responsibility to a human who has achieved their dream. {"I think that there is a responsiblity to a human who have achieved their dream.". I don't know where to start with this sentence to be honest. I've changed have to has, but this sentence needs some more work. - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:45.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And that... is about who?{That, is about who?}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Myself during the days when I dreamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Was I sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:02.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake, Hirono-kun?{did you wake? Hirono-kun.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:07.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning. It is Miyamura Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:10.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You were a student of Otowa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:12.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The school uniform look is pretty good, isn't it?{School uniform look is pretty good isn't it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You were completely out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:17.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold if you sleep in places like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:24.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's to see Hirono-kun of course.{You see, I came here to meet Hirono-kun.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:40.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If this car hadn't passed by, it would have been a good clip.{If this car hadn't passed by it would have been a good clip.} {Verified by translation, so I'm changing it. Was "If this car wouldn't have passed it wouldn't been a good clip." - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:41.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:42.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The clips that you took are good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,they're a bit hard to connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:48.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:51.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The clips are too precise so the flow between them stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I put my soul into every single clip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:57.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Put your life on the line and do the editing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Things like that cannot be accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To win at the film festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:06.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,you must aim more towards the general public.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:14.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Still, there are a lot of fans who view our work because of Kyousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:20.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's the point. So wouldn't it be right to edit while extolling Kyousuke's clips?{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:23.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kyousuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the bathroom. {going to the bathroom.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:39.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be the time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is Hirono's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:57.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for Renji-kun to arrive. Today I'll tell him the truth. {Note: We seem to be missing a line between this and the line above it. - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:13.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go to Onii-chan's house after club activities?{Can I go to Onii-chan's house after club activity?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:17.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, that deadline is close...{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I was really surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,that Hirono-kun and I were in the same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really come to school, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:35.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I also ditch like there's no tomorrow.{check, not a literal translation, but I couldn't think of anything else.}{it's fine I think}{Aiko: I'm also never here or I don't show up much either.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If so, it's obvious that we didn't notice each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:42.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When I found Hirono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:45.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wondered if I should talk to you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There are things like gathering my emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a girl, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:56.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reunion with the person that you spent Christmas night together with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to go with a romantic atmosphere?{feeling}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:01.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,We just stayed at family restaurants and karaoked until morning, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I payed for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:06.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But say, Hirono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. To tell you the truth, I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:11.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:16.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that Hirono-kun has a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:17.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:21.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy. It's nothing to be embarrassed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:24.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to have dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:27.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams or not, I'm a manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Self-proclaimed? Delusional?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Actively.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:34.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't look like it, I'm a pro that publishes in magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:35.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:36.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:38.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of manga do you draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:41.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To put it bluntly, girl manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:47.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, if you do look at it, Hirono-kun has a girlish face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only thing you're surprised about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:54.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In another words, Hirono-kun already has a career?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:55.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:57.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You are independent at that age, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:58.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're living the dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not up to there yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! You're at the prime of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:10.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the leisure of praising others, try to strive so you can be praised yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:12.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:14.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Read my manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:16.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot more arrogant things in there{lines/stuffs}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:18.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,From yesterday's me...{From the me of yesterday.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,to today's me...{To the me of today.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:16.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:19.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Chihiro isn't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:46.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:51.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hello. You took your time today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:58.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I noticed when I finished reading a book after lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What were you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:03.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That is, how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's an uninteresting book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So you were immersed in an uninteresting book?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:11.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not immersed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Something that you can't even tell your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:18.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-san is a friend, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:18.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:21.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:27.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. This should be okay to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But please keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,By all means, please.{/For sure.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:32.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely. I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.07,0:13:37.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:40.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,in truth, not reading a novel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Not reading, but...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's that you're writing one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're really mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can you show it to me?{the novel}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:53.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:57.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But it's amazing, a novel that you're writing...{that she is writing}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:00.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very displeasing reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:02.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that, it's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that it is a slightly displeasing reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:08.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's that I was thinking about if I should write my own novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-san too?{write a novel}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:14.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There was a career survey at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe being a writer is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:21.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think it will be good, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:27.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious about what kind of content the story that Asou-san writes will have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also curious about the story that Chihiro wrote-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be curious about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:32.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.{Is that right?/Really?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, please do not mention it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:38.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even in your grave or in hell, please keep silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So does that mean I'm going to hell? {right you are, you're going to hell you sinner!!}{Nuuuu! He's the one that's NOT an ass! ...Err... yet, anyways? - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:45.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But things like careers are difficult, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't difficult?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:51.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think that doing what you like is the most important thing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it. I also heard the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:57.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:57.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,An adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:01.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What does Chihiro want to become?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:02.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:04.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:05.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:10.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I want to be a novelist, but I want to write just stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:14.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just anything, I want myself of right now to make something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:18.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that Chihiro can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:19.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:20.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Although it isn't so reliable even if I guarantee that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.91,0:15:24.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.93,0:15:26.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:29.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even just hearing that makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go to school again starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:36.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't like school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,School...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:45.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:50.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to hear about school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:52.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,especially since I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:57.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My twin sister tells me often about school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:01.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When she happily does, it makes me happy just to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:02.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Your twin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:05.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, her personality is opposite of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:09.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If Onee-chan loiters without doing anything, she would surely die.{And so if Onee-chan loiters without doing anything she'll surely die.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:15.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Shindou Kei and is a first-year student of Otowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:18.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But if she's a junior-high student then there won't be a chance to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:21.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She's a high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:22.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She is Chihiro's twin right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:26.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Then Chihiro also?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:30.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If I were attending school, I would be a first-year student in high school.{If attending school, I would be a first-year student in high school.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:35.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh man, I thought she was younger until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:39.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is it okay if I call you Shindou-san from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:41.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calls me that anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:47.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then, can you just call me Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:49.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can't it be Asou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit formal, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:53.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then will it be fine as Renji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds a bit weird with "-san," so use "-kun".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:59.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But that would be embarrassing on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, we're friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:06.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. Then from now on I'll say Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:09.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:11.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:12.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:15.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's a weird sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it.{Looks like it./Looks so.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:24.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I go this way, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:26.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:26.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:27.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:28.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:33.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?{What's wrong?/What?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:43.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:44.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:46.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:47.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:48.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:49.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:51.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,let's play again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:54.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the station right after school, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:57.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow... Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:58.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Tomorrow again at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The one that was meeting with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:12.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Himura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:16.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to stay beside Chihiro then be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:28.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-san... Renji-kun said, "Let's play again tomorrow".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Not a courtesy of, "See you next time."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:33.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But this time a real promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,See you again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:48.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine tomorrow nor happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:52.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I stay here even though tomorrow comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to stay beside Chihiro then be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:06.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Be prepared" isn't something said under normal circumstances, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:35.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.{Hey./Yo.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Renji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. It is.{Yep./Yeah./It is.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:43.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:45.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:47.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:49.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to visit the shops somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:51.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If it is somewhere with few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:56.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere outside I should say; I don't like places with lots of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:04.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It is. It looks as if it was burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:06.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Asou Renji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:10.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Am I your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:13.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To be asked that again, I do wonder...{To get questioned again, I wonder.}{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:16.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I may not even be especially conscious of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:19.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then to Asou-san, what am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,At first a subject of interest. {subject of} {I moved this from the middle of the coding to the end To place it in context, "subject of interest". - Waku}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I would say that I couldn't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:29.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's not that I was worried, but just that I always wanted to meet with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:31.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a feeling like me being a little sister?{check}{okay}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:33.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was a feeling like that.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:38.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I also think that if I had a Onii-san, it would be someone like Asou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.77,0:20:39.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:42.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And so, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:45.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:47.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Deep breaths...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:53.01,ef[Default2],,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}Note: It is said that if you write the symbol of the thing that you're afraid of and swallow it, it is supposed to alleviate your fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:53.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,They say that swallowing the symbol that you write on your palm is said to help also.{check}{"They say writing the word "people" on your palm and act like eating it will help too"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:54.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:59.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I tested Asou-san for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:05.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It was to see whether or not you are a person that it's okay to tell this to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:06.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:11.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,that from then until now and even now, Asou-san hasn't changed, right?{check}{"From then until now and also now, Asou-san haven't change right?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it's not that you're another person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:15.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:18.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that you said you had a twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't something like Onee-san disguised herself and came in place of you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:27.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. I guess it isn't odd even if I'm asked if I'm another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:29.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:36.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have anterograde amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Anterograde... amnesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:43.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I can only retain memories for thirteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:49.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you look at it that way, the me from yesterday and the me from today is a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:53.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even as today passes, I cannot be me of tomorrow.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:56.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forever be this way.{her personality, her identity}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:21:57.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:21:58.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:39.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings intertwine with his feelings.
